show "lephon/lephon_2_cut1.jpg" 1:1 1:1 1.0:1.0 fade(3,linear) normal
move "lephon/lephon_2_cut1.jpg" 700:0 35 sineout

say "Although she was young, \"Compassion\" was determined to have Faith's head.
Faith saw this, saw that L was still trying to help her teacher, and so went to L instead."

play "ruffle.ogg" 2.0

