hide "lephon/lephon_2_cut1.jpg" fade(0.1,linear)

say "—and using her spear, she took the limb from L."

play "ring.ogg" 3.0

say "L looked at the limb she'd lost as the 2nd dropped it callously to float through space, 
and she soon felt her consciousness fading. 
Nell shivered and froze on seeing this—so Faith returned to her."

say "Faith took Nell's shoulder—
drew back her spear again—
and, quickly—"

show "white.png" 0.5:0.5 0.5:0.5 2000:960 fade(0,linear) normal
