say "She ran the spear through the young woman's body, the seams of reality 
warping upon contact—undoing \"who\" Nell \"was\"."

say "So, in almost an instant, Nell had gone.
The child meanwhile... went still, and cold."

wait 0.25

show "lephon/lephon_1_cut2.jpg" 1:0.5 1:0.5 1.0:1.0 fade(0,linear) normal
